Steve I have purchased from them once when I was just getting back into woodworking. The selection is amazing, the quality was fine, the price with shipping (and without) was high. They are not outrageous, but they are high. If I needed a quanity of special wood (read exotic) for a special project, I wouldn’t hesitate to give them a try. There are a lot of sellers out there and most try to give good service as bad news travels fast.
